sentence as input, first letter as cap, print first letter of each word followed by dot
program:

s=" lahari venkatesh "
print("Original:",s)
a=s.title()
print("After Capitalize:",a)
b=a.split()
c='.'.join(word[0] for word in b)
print(c)

OUTPUT:
Original: lahari venkatesh
After Capitalize: Lahari Venkatesh
L.V
